title: An Angel Fell [A Good Omens Fansong]
author: Nine Aetharia
comment:
Am I the only one person who needs this masterpiece in spotify? 
I'm serious 
I need this in my playlist! 
It's just the most beautiful song that i've ever heard. And I can't believe the gorgeous way that you expressed all Aziraphale's feelings for Crowley. Beautiful it's not enough to describe it.

Hey, so I’m kind of late but- 
Can I say this is one of the most wonderful Aziraphale to Crowley things had anyone made, ‘you are the world’s longest kept secret’ ‘sweet like a sonnet’ ‘that beat twice for treason’ ‘Yet id rise with them’ 
I’m kinda close to crying, and you bring the nightingale into there with the Garden

I think you should know, I sang this to my friend over the phone, and she was sobbing by the end. She said she was fine until the part where the lyrics ask "have you ever loved someone so much, you would do anything, be anything?"

The lyrics and your voice. 😭💕
Hearing this song I felt that thing opposite of spooky. I feel love. 💗💗💗
Thank you for sharing. 😘
If they played this in the last episode I would have cried for months
